originalText.text: Dr. Jill Fishburne-Mayer saved my life. Without her I would have had surgeries that I didn't need. She listened to my gynecological issues the first time I went to her and throughout my journey with her. I am in better health than when I first saw her. I can't thank her enough. And I can't thank my husband's cousin who referred me to Dr. Mayer.

originalText.text:
The epitome of a fabulous doctor.  I have had alot of experience with doctors  and Jill Fishbane-Mayer is by far the top of the chart. Five stars is just not enough.
I have had the pleasure of being a patient of Jill's for over 32 years.  I have total trust and fath  in her
excellent professional  skills but also as a kind, wonderful person.  I have recommended friends to her and they have all felt the same.  I only wish more doctors could take her example.  I have always been so informed of any procedure she will do.  Five stars in my book at least.
